          <td>Hurricane Laura — Category 4, made landfall near Lake Charles</td>
          <td>~$10B insured losses; southwest LA market began showing stress</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>August 2021</td>
          <td>Hurricane Ida — Category 4, made landfall in Lafourche Parish</td>
          <td>~$23B insured losses; triggered carrier exit cascade</td>
